{"tid":2256311,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國泰迷：染紅如吸毒必衰亡","createTime":"2020-10-24T08:57:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-24T09:04:33.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c2613973a932db11d7359a6c5d205469f3480e43","tid":2256311,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T08:57:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201022/PYIO35W5CFGMFAZWV7ODFVLKUQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201022%2FPYIO35W5CFGMFAZWV7ODFVLKUQ%2F&d=ob16Qiumsg8bXj4Ev1LzLD2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=9c83315e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201022%2FPYIO35W5CFGMFAZWV7ODFVLKUQ%2F&h=1c0f0dd1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201022/PYIO35W5CFGMFAZWV7ODFVLKUQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n國泰迷：染紅如吸毒必衰亡<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】從「惡晒」到「因航」，國泰航空陪伴香港翱翔74年，如今卻與香港變成命運共同體，同步衰落。有蒐集國泰飛機模型10年的航空迷慨嘆，「好似你追緊嘅明星走咗去吸毒，自甘墮落咁」，認為紅色資本滲透是國泰致命傷，「同香港一樣返唔到轉頭。」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：港歷來最大規模裁員  國泰斬港龍 吊命兩年半<br />\n<br />\n24歲飛機迷Jack逾十年前開始節衣縮食蒐集飛機模型，。。。。。。。。。，「好有歸屬感，你旅行返嚟坐國泰，聽到講廣東話嘅crew（機組人員），會覺得自己真係返緊屋企。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/BScyylPYmISjVgonQxYFXtA964U=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZKZXFG3XPJCSTF7LC6SLAT7Q74.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FBScyylPYmISjVgonQxYFXtA964U%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZKZXFG3XPJCSTF7LC6SLAT7Q74.jpg&h=f4ac80f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■飛機迷Jack（左）十年前開始儲飛機模型，見證國泰漸漸離開世界一流航空舞台。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。，「到𠵱家都只係短短六年，又要裁員，一半飛機又擺晒沙漠，其實都幾大落差。」他搖頭嘆喟：「必然嘅，同香港𠵱家狀態一樣。」他相信國泰的衰亡始於股權逐漸染紅，「慢慢溝淡、稀釋，原本可以自己決定未來發展，𠵱家變咗俾人左右你決定。」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：月燒15億元  旅遊氣泡續命 投行上調評級<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/FeBdfYxkXPtSllADIlrf2muzqW4=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/Q2DRARJJRZDSNAYVYT4IS725IU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FFeBdfYxkXPtSllADIlrf2muzqW4%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQ2DRARJJRZDSNAYVYT4IS725IU.jpg&h=a343ccd9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■相比設計簡約的新標誌，阿Jack更喜歡舊版的國泰標誌。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n常客冀保留港式價值觀<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。國泰被武漢肺炎「感染」得體無完膚，劉晉明白企業於疫潮下生存很困難，但他認為管理層考慮出路時要以人為本，多諒解前線，思考管治方針應否有轉變。<br />\n<br />\n劉指出，國泰不僅是一間商業機構，更是背負香港人身份的企業，「國泰好似香港縮影」，應保持着重服務、追求質素等價值觀，別讓一些港人相信的價值消失於無形。"},{"pid":"b387cb0f347bc9b0ed6240b393976d6503b54400","tid":2256311,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T09:00:23.000Z","msg":"撐泰國<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9baf9e7092bb2deb7129eb477cd685504e47135d","tid":2256311,"uid":27530,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T09:02:53.000Z","msg":"國泰係一間香港航空公司，僅此而已。"},{"pid":"d960198cbb2c6da59a11210d3938e9628d5a684e","tid":2256311,"uid":59976,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T09:04:33.000Z","msg":"根本就死不足惜，唔抵可憐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}